reviewText: Who doesn't love the pirates who don't do anything?! Great lessons for children.
Veggie Tales are always so much Fun! My grandkids love them and so do I !!
I thought it was the full length movie, nothing in comments that led me to beleive otherwise. I was dissapointed. It is in good condition however.
I bought this for my grandchildren. It is their all time favorite veggie tale movie.  It's a cute, wholesome movie with a pirate theme.
Great little movie for kids, very entertaining for adults as well. My 2 year old loves it, and after watching it a hundred times, I can still enjoy it as well.
